From: Ruan Zhengwang <zhengwang.ruan@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 30 Jul 2013 15:15:15 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] fsl-e600: Add MPC8641D platform

Set primary_phb_addr explicitly to make fsl_pci_setup() happy.

Signed-off-by: Ruan Zhengwang <zhengwang.ruan@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/platforms/86xx/mpc86xx_hpcn.c |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/platforms/86xx/mpc86xx_hpcn.c b/arch/powerpc/platforms/86xx/mpc86xx_hpcn.c
index 8bedac2..114e9e0 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/platforms/86xx/mpc86xx_hpcn.c
+++ b/arch/powerpc/platforms/86xx/mpc86xx_hpcn.c
@@ -77,6 +77,7 @@ mpc86xx_hpcn_setup_arch(void)
 		ppc_md.progress("mpc86xx_hpcn_setup_arch()", 0);
 
 #ifdef CONFIG_PCI
+	primary_phb_addr = 0x8000;
 	for_each_node_by_type(np, "pci")
 		fsl_pci_setup(np);
 
